      <title>哈里斯誓言在辩论前推动政策，取消最低工资标准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/harris-vows-to-end-subminimum-wages-in-policy-push-before-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯承诺取消小费工人的最低工资标准，并在周二与唐纳德·特朗普进行首次辩论之前加大取消小费税的力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/harris-vows-to-end-subminimum-wages-in-policy-push-before-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 13:34:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默将就养老金削减问题与工党反对派正面交锋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/starmer-set-to-face-down-labour-rebels-on-pensioner-benefit-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 计划平息工党议员对他取消大多数养老金领取者一项主要福利的决定所提出的抗议，而他的助手警告称，如果改变政策，英国将面临更难以接受的公共财政修复选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/starmer-set-to-face-down-labour-rebels-on-pensioner-benefit-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 13:03:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳副总统提交竞选申请，希望选举能够和平进行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/ghana-vice-president-expects-peaceful-poll-as-he-files-candidacy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳副总统马哈穆杜·巴武米亚表示，他预计 12 月举行的选举将是和平的，他已提交文件，准备竞选这个西非国家的下一任领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/ghana-vice-president-expects-peaceful-poll-as-he-files-candidacy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:56:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>行业组织称澳大利亚应解决矿工的担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/australia-should-address-concerns-of-mining-industry-group-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚矿产委员会首席执行官塔尼亚·康斯特布尔表示，澳大利亚应该解决与环境审批程序有关的问题，并强调业界担心新矿的开发将变得越来越具有挑战性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/australia-should-address-concerns-of-mining-industry-group-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:25:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德拉吉指出欧盟计划对境外碳排放征税存在风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/draghi-flags-risks-for-eu-plan-to-tax-carbon-beyond-its-borders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行前行长马里奥·德拉吉表示，欧洲对进口碳排放定价的大胆计划存在风险，可能导致其无效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/draghi-flags-risks-for-eu-plan-to-tax-carbon-beyond-its-borders</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:24:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉脱维亚军方称坠毁的俄罗斯无人机是 Shahed 式的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/latvia-military-says-crashed-russian-drone-was-shahed-style</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉脱维亚最高军事指挥官表示，在该国领土上坠毁的俄罗斯无人机是伊朗设计的型号，当局呼吁北约盟国加强防空力量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/latvia-military-says-crashed-russian-drone-was-shahed-style</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界上最古老的游击队重新对石油公司发起战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/world-s-oldest-guerrilla-force-revives-its-war-on-oil-companies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚叛军重新发起对石油工业的战争，发动了一系列管道袭击，导致原油泄漏到河流中，黑烟滚滚冲上天空。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/world-s-oldest-guerrilla-force-revives-its-war-on-oil-companies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙战争重创经济 以色列财政部下调增长预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/israel-s-finance-ministry-cuts-growth-forecast-as-war-in-gaza-hits-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列财政部大幅下调了对 2024 年经济增长的预测，凸显了与哈马斯近一年的战争给该国经济带来的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/israel-s-finance-ministry-cuts-growth-forecast-as-war-in-gaza-hits-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:41:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德拉吉称若无更多资金和联合债务，欧盟自身将面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/draghi-says-eu-in-danger-without-massive-spending-and-joint-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行前行长马里奥·德拉吉呼吁欧盟每年额外投资 8000 亿欧元（8840 亿美元），并承诺定期发行共同债券，以使欧盟在与中国和美国的竞争中更具竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/draghi-says-eu-in-danger-without-massive-spending-and-joint-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:02:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国超级富豪打破掩护，攻击工党的非英国居民计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/uk-s-non-doms-rally-against-labour-reforms-as-crackdown-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莱斯利·麦克劳德-米勒的职业生涯部分是在幕后工作，在一些世界上最著名的亿万富翁控制的公司工作。最近，他与超级富豪有了一份新工作，而且非常公开。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/uk-s-non-doms-rally-against-labour-reforms-as-crackdown-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 06:58:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
